@node "Introduction" "Introduction"
@{PAR}
When getting Hollywood, the famous \"MultimediaApplicatinLayer\" the wish to create a game grew.
@{PAR}
This is \"AlienAttack\" a clone of \"SpaceInvader\" done with Hollywood2.
@{PAR}
It uses Sprites, internal tables and is created in a modular way.
@{PAR}
Even if finishing this project lasted a little bit longer than previously expected, it was fun programing.
@{PAR}
@endnode

@node "Req" "Requirements"
@{PAR}
You need a relatively powerful amigacompatible computersystem to start the game. A native 68040 might be insuficient.
@{PAR}
There are executables for Classic-AmigaOS, AmigaOS4, MorphOS and AROS
@{PAR}
RAM: 16MB
@{PAR}
PNG-Datatype
@{PAR}
Screen: 24Bit 640x480.
@{PAR}
@{PAR}
@endnode

