@node "Control" "Controls"
@{PAR}
The menus:
@{PAR}
@{PAR}
Main menu:
@{PAR}
   1. Start
@{PAR}
            The game itself begins.
@{PAR}
            Via <ESC> you get back to the main menu.
@{PAR}
@{PAR}
   2. Settings
@{PAR}
            You can adjust the folloing things:
@{PAR}
                                                                 @{PAR}
            Difficulty - 3 steps                                 @{PAR}
            change keyboard-layout                               @{PAR}
            view keyboard-layout                                 @{PAR}
            enter playername                                     @{PAR}
            save settings                                        @{PAR}
            load settings                                        @{PAR}
            restore internal default values                      @{PAR}
@{PAR}
@{PAR}
@{PAR}
   3. Highscores
@{PAR}
            Here you can view highscores for each type of difficulty.  @{PAR}
            You can delete the highscore-files.                        @{PAR}
@{PAR}

   4. End the game
@{PAR}
            You return to your System.
@{PAR}

@{PAR}
@{PAR}
@{PAR}
Predefined keyboard-layout:
@{PAR}
@{PAR}
Move Left:       Arrow left
@{PAR}
@{PAR}
Move Right:      Arrow right
@{PAR}
@{PAR}
Fire:            Arrow up
@{PAR}
@{PAR}
Beam Left:       y
@{PAR}
@{PAR}
Beam Right:      x
@{PAR}
Note: It is only possible to do 3 beams per Level.
@{PAR}
@endnode

